				<p class="text-stone-200 type-body-lg mb-4" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">If this resonates — if you sense that success has not satisfied the deeper ache — there is a next step.</p>
				<p class="text-stone-200 type-body-lg mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">The Kingdom Messenger Collective is where heart becomes shared journey, and message becomes movement. We are building a pastorally stewarded container for leaders who refuse to sacrifice intimacy for impact.</p>
